reviewText: Great movies but enjoyed the books more.
I bought this set for the value, the blu-ray and value.  I love both movies and would recommend it as a good purchase.
Tom Hanks is awesome as usual, two great work's of fiction. The Blu-ray disc came in excellent shape and quality.
To good a deal to pass up!
Great spellbinding entertainment.  Extremely thought provoking.
I love both of these movies!
